# FILE: Caddyfile
# PHOENIX PROTOCOL - UNIFIED GATEWAY CONFIG V7.0 (SSE FIX)
# 1. FIX (JURISTI): Added a 'transport http' block with an extended 'read_timeout' of 10 minutes to the 'api.juristi.tech' proxy.
# 2. REASON: Resolves critical 'net::ERR_CONNECTION_CLOSED' errors by preventing Caddy from prematurely terminating the long-lived Server-Sent Events (SSE) stream.
# 3. SCOPE: This change is targeted only at the Juristi API and does not affect the Haveri project configuration.

